('ONET-FOOD_SCIENCE_TECHNICIANS', 'source_onet_food_science_technicians', 'Food Science Technicians', 'Food Science Technicians is an imported ONET role/occupation concept. It needs TALLENTIN normalization before production routing.', 'role_title', 'Work with food scientists or technologists to perform standardized qualitative and quantitative tests to determine physical or chemical properties of food or beverage products. Includes technicians who assist in research and development of production technology, quality control, packaging, processing, and use of foods.', ARRAY['Beer Brewer','Biotechnician','Bottle House QC Technician (Bottle House Quality Control Technician)','Butter Fat Tester','Central Laboratory Technician (CLT)','Cheese Tester','Cream Tester','Dairy and Food Laboratory Assistant (Dairy and Food Lab Assist)','Dairy Laboratory Technician (Dairy Lab Tech)','Dairy Technician (Dairy Tech)','Dairy Technologist','Dairy Tester','Data Control Assistant','Fermentologist','Flavor Technician (Flavor Tech)','Food Analyst','Food Products Tester','Food QC Technician (Food Quality Control Technician)','Food Quality Technician (Food Quality Tech)','Food Safety QA Tech (Food Safety Quality Assurance Technician)','Food Safety Technician (Food Safety Tech)','Food Science Tech (Food Science Technician)','Food Taster','Food Technician (Food Tech)','Food Tester','Fruit Tester','Juice Standardizer','Juice Tester','Laboratory Assistant (Lab Assistant)','Laboratory Technician (Lab Tech)','Malt Specifications Control Assistant','Milk Tester','QA Lab Tech (Quality Assurance Lab Technician)','QC Tech (Quality Assurance Technician)','QC Tech (Quality Control Technician)','Quality Analyst','Quality Assurance Analyst (QA Analyst)','Quality Tech (Quality Technician)','Research Technician (Research Tech)','Seed Analyst','Sensory Scientist','Sugarcane Research Technician (Sugarcane Research Tech)','Taste Tester','Test Baker','Yeast Culture Developer']::text[], ARRAY['Food Science Tech