('ONET-OCCUPATIONAL_HEALTH_AND_SAFETY_SPECIALISTS', 'source_onet_occupational_health_and_safety_specialists', 'Occupational Health and Safety Specialists', 'Occupational Health and Safety Specialists is an imported ONET role/occupation concept. It needs TALLENTIN normalization before production routing.', 'role_title', 'Review, evaluate, and analyze work environments and design programs and procedures to control, eliminate, and prevent disease or injury caused by chemical, physical, and biological agents or ergonomic factors. May conduct inspections and enforce adherence to laws and regulations governing the health and safety of individuals. May be employed in the public or private sector.', ARRAY['Analysis Safety Inspector','Cause Analyst','Certified Indoor Environmentalist','Certified Industrial Hygienist (CIH)','Chemical Hygiene Officer','Construction Safety Manager','Consumer Safety Inspector','Dining Service Inspector','EHS Officer (Environmental Health and Safety Officer)','EHS Specialist (Environmental Health and Safety Specialist)','Environmental Health Inspector','Environmental Health Sanitarian','Environmental Health Technologist','Environmental Protection Inspector','Environmental Protection Officer','Field Health Officer','Food and Drug Inspector','Food Inspector','Hazardous Waste Management Specialist','Health and Safety Analyst','Health and Safety Inspector','Health Care Facilities Inspector','Health Inspector','Health Sanitarian','Health Specialist','Industrial Hygiene Consultant','Industrial Hygienist','Industrial Hygienist Consultant','Industrial Safety and Health Specialist','Industrial Waste Inspector','Mine Safety and Health Inspector','Mortician Investigator','Occupational Safety and Health Inspector','OHS Consultant (Occupational Health and Safety Consultant)','OHS Specialist (Occupational Health and Safety Specialist)','OSHA Inspector (Occupational Safety and Health Administration Inspector)','Public Health Inspector','Public Health Service Of